## Description {#details}

A pointer to another debug information entry.

An instance of this class can also be used as a proxy for a debug information entry not yet defined (ie. types.)

Definition at line 319 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/die-h">DIE.h</a>.
